name: Might Of The Republic
Lore: 'Despite its current reputation, the Republic still has able citizens that are willing to try and fight the injustices before them.',
Text: 'Once per game, retrieve 1 Force for each of your senators at Galactic Senate. (Immune to Sense.) OR Take one senator (or Coruscant Guard, Sei Taria or Mas Amedda) into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
